OL,3,CTowie star Jake Hall post-mortem fails
OL,4,Cto determine cause of death
OL,6,FA post-mortem examination of the Only
OL,7,FWay Is Essex star Jake Hall ` who died
OL,8,Fsuddenly in Mallorca aged 35 last
OL,9,Fmonth ` could not determine the exact
OL,10,Fcause of his death, an inquest opening
OL,11,Fhas heard.
OL,13,FHall was found dead with head injuries
OL,14,Fat a holiday villa on the island
OL,15,Ffollowing a collision with a glass
OL,16,Fdoor on 6 May, East London Coroner's
OL,17,FCourt was told on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
