OL,3,CTowie star Jake Hall post-mortem fails
OL,4,Cto determine cause of death
OL,6,FShe recalled meeting Hall at a bar
OL,7,Faged 16, stating that he looked like
OL,8,Fhe had "stepped straight out of a
OL,9,FRalph Lauren" advert with his sleeves
OL,10,Frolled up and a red sweatshirt tied
OL,11,Fover his shoulders.
